<MOLayout title={title}>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Main</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            What's Misty Ore ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            Misty Ore is a mod for Minecraft java edition.
        </p>
        <p>
            Misty Ore, This mod adds several new ores for a new experience in the game. Some ores can be used to craft tools and armor.
        </p>
        <p>
            We created this mod to add a variety of new ores, items, tools, and armor.  To add to the experience of playing in the world of minecraft becomes more fun.   
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            How is Misty ore created ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            The Misty Ore mod is created by adding scripts to several files that have been included in the Minecraft Development Kit, such as scripts, assets, and the addition of json files.
        </p>
        <p>
            This mod is built using the Forge framework.
        </p>
    </div>  
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            How often does Misty Ore update version ?
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <p>
            For version updates, every two weeks or once a month.
        </p>
        <p>
            Regarding the mod version update, it is actually not always in line with what was mentioned above, because if we have a new project, the update may be delayed.   
        </p>
    </div>  
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>
            Changelog
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <div class="version-new">
            <h3>Version: 0.1.1</h3>
        </div>
        <h4>
            New
        </h4>
        <h5>
            Items :
        </h5>
        <div class="changelog">
            <ul>
                <li>Amethyst</li>
                <li>Shadowite</li>
                <li>Mystic Glowstone</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h5>
            Blocks :
        </h5>
        <div class="changelog">
            <ul>
                <li>Amethyst Ore</li>
                <li>Shadowite Ore</li>
                <li>Amethyst Block</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h5>
            Armors :
        </h5>
        <div class="changelog">
            <ul>
                <li>Mystic Glowstone Helmet</li>
                <li>Mystic Glowstone Chestplate</li>
                <li>Mystic Glowstone Leggings</li>
                <li>Mystic Glowstone Boots</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h5>
            Tools :
        </h5>
        <div class="changelog">
            <ul>
                <li>Shadowite Sword</li>
                <li>Shadowite Axe</li>
                <li>Shadowite Pickaxe</li>
                <li>Shadowite Hoe</li>
                <li>Shadowite Shovel</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>      
    <div class="container-h2">
        <h2>Download Misty Ore mod</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="container-teks">
        <div class="container-downloads">
